Philippines Watching Market for Debt Management Opportunities

-- B y   M a x   E s t a y o
-- 
2011-10-12T03:30:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/philippines-watching-market-for-debt-management-opportunities.html
The  Philippines  is monitoring
financial markets for further opportunities for liability
management, including reducing its foreign-currency exposure,
Finance Secretary Cesar Purisima told reporters today in  Manila .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Max Estayo in Manila at 
